                          </span></div><div><span id="digesttext"/></div><span class="hidden"><h2>Digest Key</h2></span></div><hr/><span class="hidden"><h2>Bill Text</h2></span><span class="Resolution" title="source: /caml:MeasureDoc/caml:Resolution&#xA;    "><span class="Resolved" id="id_53D5D4FD-0C44-4EAD-9E7F-A0FCF7D10FBA"><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">Resolved by the Senate of the State of California, That the President pro Tempore of the Senate appoint a Special Committee to wait upon his Excellency, the Governor, and inform him that the Senate is duly organized for the 2025–26 Regular Session and is now ready to receive any communication he may have to make to this House. </div></span></span></div></body></html>
